Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:34.61,OP1_English,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched the coin as I flicked it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:41.72,OP1_English,,0000,0000,0000,,Heads is GO, Tails is STAY. But first, let me hear your answer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:50.07,OP1_English,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:58.15,OP1_English,,0000,0000,0000,,The angels judges me as they smile
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:05.83,OP1_English,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost! No one's going to hold your hand!
