Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.99,0:00:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Kamijou Touma, am a misfortunate person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should be obvious if you were to take a look at the past seven days of the Daihaseisai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the day after that whole mess got cleaned up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally walked in on Komoe-sensei changing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got headbutted by Fukiyose Seiri after her unreasonably fast recovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got whacked by a rubber ball that Himegami Aisa threw at me from her wheelchair,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and while I was being forced to partner with Misaka Mikoto in the folk dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got drop-kicked in the back of the head by Shirai Kuroko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, I had a pretty miserable time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, once again, I am a misfortunate—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Visitor Numbers lottery, a tradition for the last day of the Daihaseisai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number you have selected is first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your prize is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 5-night 7-day pair vacation to Northern Italy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A vacation to Italy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be getting repetitive, but I am a misfortunate person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a passport!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a passport?{trololol, normal cutesy scene for the first time in how many eps?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would happen from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only two days till we leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't apply for a passport now and—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my passport!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so I've been overseas before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma Touma! I have something like that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you don't have any stamps or anything in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How on earth did you get all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have that, am I allowed to go on vacation with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I feel that it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm supposed to be misfortunate person...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't forget anything, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wallet, passports, airplane tickets...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Required documents, change of clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting so worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can just enjoy this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! It's my 5-day 7-night Northern Italy vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time in a long, long while, I get to feel fortunate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:16.33,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, run Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need some proper clothes to get on the plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Touma, you're going to buy me clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1.5 kilometers to the shopping area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,28 minutes until the plane lifts off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I knew I was misfortunate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean sure is closeby...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be more correct to say it surrounds us rather than it's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:05:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chioggia is an island city surrounded by the Adriatic Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we landed at the airport I had to buy a ton of safety pins,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then we got ditched by a scammer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a bit rough on the way, but we finally got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to survive in the globalized society of this day and age, you should be able to speak at least three languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This weirdass sister just said "this day and age" and "at least" to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can eat after we drop off our things at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, you don't have to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, is that a real basilica?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:57.01,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, food is pretty nice too, but let's go to Venetia once we check in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try a gondola at least once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Index...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'm going to be the one who's lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ciao! Il qual c'è problema?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.21,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Non si parla italiano?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.61,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't speak Italian?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Là si trova un ristorante, c'è une villetto un giapponese.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:29.50,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there is a restaurant, and there's a Japanese person living nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Wait, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Scusi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.40,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lui è mio amico.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.29,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}La ringrazia per la sua gentilezza.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:40.32,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your kind help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Prego. Ciao!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:42.96,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, bye then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, should I have refrained from doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared to me that you were in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Orsola?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a 5-night 7-day Northern Italy vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you here, Orsola?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be in London?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I've lived until just a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was some trouble during my conversion from the Roman Catholics to the Church of England.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bags are still here, but people from the Amakusa Church have been helping me move things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Amakusa church? Those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, might you be shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I came here with Index, but she disappeared somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been fate to meet you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I ask you to help me sort out my luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I kind of need to look for Index...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if you're looking for Index-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, Touma, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, the gelato here is so delicious, yet it's actually really cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found her not long ago staring through the window of a gelato shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I asked a friend to bring her back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You abandoned me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Orsola, when's lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the guy the acting Pope has his eye on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how strong is he really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only asking that because you weren't involved in Orsola's rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who attacked the Roman Catholic stronghold of battle nuns, alone and unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:09:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say he also saw the Priestess-sama naked and got sent flying with a single blow from her Shichiten Shitou,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he didn't even need a bandage after...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that messed up impression of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, this looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this is okay, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't helped you with your moving at all yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accommodating you comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll gladly accept then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuwa, how did the hot towel plan go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! It's too early to see results!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first step is making a good impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this too unnatural?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.23,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they eating with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the middle of training right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they need to follow a strict diet and preparation methodology.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, start before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.82,0:10:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How can this taste so good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be 500 times better than anything Touma cooks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to say that, but this is so good I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!! Delicious!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, is the main focus of your trip going to be Venice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the plan, but I couldn't get in touch with the tour guide...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I highly recommend you see Venice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Water Capital", "Queen of the Adriatic Sea"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful that people give it a lot of names like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll take a look then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Index...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll wrap up the plates next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orsola!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you say the pile of newspapers was?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice and sound of water combo must mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all dirty now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a shower then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you must be tired from the flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoop! So this bathroom is a trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A voice from here too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, there can't be two bathrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is the correct room, one isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, what's with this ultimate decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... no, left...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shower sound is only coming from the left...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, something occurred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I think of the simple solution of knocking to check?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one was the bathroom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Orsola!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot air is coming out of some weird wand thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, both right and left were bathrooms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two bathrooms in this place??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One's for normal use, and the other is meant for use by the church...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since I'm moving house, it's not being used for baptism right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why aren't you even apologizing after seeing us naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, you see, Index-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The newspapers—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it in your hands then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the hard work, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for taking up so much of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are your plans now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about coming sightseeing with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you plan to head to your hotel soon, so asking me to come along would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one too many people for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too many?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! You don't need to know about that, Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I was thinking of looking around and saying farewell to Chioggia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived here a long time, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd rather not have you see me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure my emotions will get the better of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my leave here then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get the opportunity, I'd love to show you my place in London too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, same to you, if you end up in Japan again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need to clean your room before that, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A-A-T-R.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.70,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(633,594)}Shift mark left
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orsola!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Index noticed it....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who and how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-S-I C-B-I{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.98,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(633,588)}Turn your blade on yourself {falcooooon PUNCH!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the sniper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiming at us from a far off point means that the person knows what the situation is where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then regardless of where the person is, my Spell Intercept will hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring out the escape boat now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll kill the woman on the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be the sniper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, this is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they hide this under the canal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orsola, get in the boat for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can such a huge ship sail in the canal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem we're leaving land...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is this ship going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear they're looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't look like we'd survive that kind of fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hide for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait for a change to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, what the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they go out of their way to create such a huge ship to attack us with?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys looked like they were wearing the same kind of clothes as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it would appear they're from the Roman Catholic Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess this must be about the Book of Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That affair should be been settled after the Church of England took me in...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.39,0:21:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this ship wasn't their main base, but only one of a larger fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the canal was too small for them to make a formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Index okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be able to use her cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I guess it isn't turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, do I even get a signal in the middle of the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Hide somewhere, Orsola!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where could I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just lock—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnese?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnese has a crazy plan in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A secret organization, "Queen of the Adriatic"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Tatemiya? Even the Amakusa Church is involved?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.95,0:23:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Queen's Fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross, the story begins.
